Prescription Http Server
========================

[![Dependencies](https://david-dm.org/josephmoniz/prescription-http-server.png)](https://david-dm.org/josephmoniz/prescription-http-server)

Prescription FRP wrapper for creating http servers.

Example
-------
Hello world:
```javascript
var HttpServer = require("prescription-http-server");
var Observable = require("prescription").Observable;
var server     = new HttpServer();

server.listen(3000).requests.subscribe(function(pair) {
    Observable.returnValue("Hello World!").subscribe(pair.response);
});

```
